<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>Nexus - Agentic AI Framework</title>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
        <style>
            :root {
                --primary-color: #1a237e;
                --secondary-color: #6efff5;
                --tertiary-color: #ff6e9c;
                --background-color: #f0f2f5;
            }
            body {
                font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #333;
                background: var(--background-color);
                overflow-x: hidden;
            }
            .bg-primary { background-color: var(--primary-color); }
            .bg-secondary { background-color: var(--secondary-color); }
            .bg-tertiary { background-color: var(--tertiary-color); }
            .text-primary { color: var(--primary-color); }
            .text-secondary { color: var(--secondary-color); }
            .text-tertiary { color: var(--tertiary-color); }
            .border-primary { border-color: var(--primary-color); }
            .border-secondary { border-color: var(--secondary-color); }
            .border-tertiary { border-color: var(--tertiary-color); }
            .parallax {
                background-attachment: fixed;
                background-position: center;
                background-repeat: no-repeat;
                background-size: cover;
            }
            .animate-fade-in {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
                transition: opacity 0.5s ease-out, transform 0.5s ease-out;
            }
            .animate-fade-in.visible {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
            .hero {
                position: relative;
                overflow: hidden;
            }
            .hero::before {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                bottom: 0;
                background: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(26, 35, 126, 0.7), rgba(110, 255, 245, 0.7));
                z-index: 1;
            }
            .hero-content {
                position: relative;
                z-index: 2;
            }
            .feature-card, .design-card, .roadmap-card {
                transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;
                padding: 2rem;
                border-radius: 1rem;
                background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
                box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            }
            .feature-card:hover, .design-card:hover, .roadmap-card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
                box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            }
            .container {
                max-width: 1200px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 0 1rem;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
        <header class="bg-primary text-white p-4 fixed w-full z-10">
            <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Nexus</h1>
                <nav>
                    <ul class="flex space-x-4">
                        <li><a href="#features" class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors">Features</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#design" class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors">Design</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#roadmap" class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors">Roadmap</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/login" class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors">Login</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/register" class="hover:text-secondary transition-colors">Register</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main class="flex-grow pt-16">
            <section class="hero parallax h-screen flex items-center" style="background-image: url('/AI.webp')">
                <div class="container mx-auto text-center hero-content">
                    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white animate-fade-in">Nexus: Agentic AI Framework</h1>
                    <p class="text-xl mb-10 text-white animate-fade-in">Revolutionize complex task solving with advanced AI collaboration and seamless tool integration</p>
                    <a href="/app" class="bg-secondary text-primary px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-colors animate-fade-in">Get Started</a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="features" class="py-20 bg-white">
                <div class="container mx-auto">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-primary animate-fade-in">Key Features</h2>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                        <div class="feature-card animate-fade-in">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Multi-agent Collaboration</h3>
                            <p>Harness the collective intelligence of multiple AI agents working in harmony to tackle complex challenges.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card animate-fade-in">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Dynamic Tool Selection</h3>
                            <p>Automatically identify and deploy the most effective tools for each unique task, optimizing efficiency and results.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card animate-fade-in">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">External API Integration</h3>
                            <p>Seamlessly connect with a wide array of external services and data sources to enhance capabilities and insights.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card animate-fade-in">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Task Decomposition</h3>
                            <p>Break down complex tasks into manageable subtasks for efficient processing and parallel execution.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card animate-fade-in">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Adaptive Learning</h3>
                            <p>Continuously evolve and refine performance through experience, feedback, and cutting-edge machine learning techniques.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card animate-fade-in">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Real-time Decision Making</h3>
                            <p>Make informed decisions on-the-fly using real-time data analysis and predictive modeling.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="design" class="py-20 bg-gray-100 parallax" style="background-image: url('/design-bg.jpg')">
                <div class="container mx-auto">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-white animate-fade-in">Design Considerations</h2>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                        <div class="design-card animate-fade-in">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">AI Models</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
                                <li>Multiple AI provider integration</li>
                                <li>Model pairing for optimal performance</li>
                                <li>Meta-learning for quick adaptation</li>
                                <li>Federated learning for privacy</li>
                                <li>Fine-tuning for specific tasks</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="design-card animate-fade-in">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Tool Integration</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
                                <li>Standardized interface for tools</li>
                                <li>Automatic tool discovery</li>
                                <li>Version control for configurations</li>
                                <li>A/B testing for tool performance</li>
                                <li>Plugin system for new tools</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="design-card animate-fade-in">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Architecture</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
                                <li>Modular design for easy extension</li>
                                <li>Microservices-based approach</li>
